Reasoning: The paper deals with automatic data extraction from charts using deep neural networks, which is a problem in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves object detection, text recognition, and object matching, which are common topics in the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) techniques for text recognition, which falls under the sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the paper involves information retrieval techniques for data extraction, which is a topic in the sub-category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
